# Networking

This folder contains my notes and practical exercises covering networking fundamentals.

Topics include:

* OSI Model
* TCP/IP
* IP Addressing & Subnetting
* Routing & Switching
* Ports & Protocols
* DNS & DHCP
* HTTP & HTTPS
* Firewalls
* VPNs
* Wireshark
* Network Troubleshooting

The goal of this section is to build a strong understanding of networking concepts and how they apply to cybersecurity.
